#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:172
msgid "Found my keys in 2 hours!"
msgstr "Leidsin oma võtmed 2 tunniga!"

#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:173
msgid ""
"I dropped my car keys while jogging in Central Park. Posted a report here, "
"and someone found them and contacted me via secure chat within two hours. "
"Absolute lifesaver!"
msgstr ""
"Kaotasin auto võtmed Central Parkis sörkides. Postitasin siia teatise ning "
"keegi leidis need ja võttis minuga turvalise vestluse kaudu kahe tunni "
"jooksul ühendust. Tõeline elupäästja!"

#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:179
msgid "Lost Car Keys"
msgstr "Kaotatud autovõtmed"

#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:189
msgid "Max is back home safely"
msgstr "Max on turvaliselt kodus tagasi"

#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:190
msgid ""
"Our golden retriever Max escaped through the backyard fence. The community "
"support here was outstanding. A neighbor three blocks away posted a photo of "
"him under 'Found Pets'."
msgstr ""
"Meie kuldne retriiver Max pääses läbi tagahoovi aia plehku. Kogukonna toetus "
"siin oli erakordne. Kolme kvartali kaugusel elav naaber postitas tema foto "
"leitud lemmikloomade alla."

#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:196
msgid "Lost Golden Retriever"
msgstr "Kaotatud kuldne retriiver"

#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:206
msgid "Safe and secure exchange"
msgstr "Turvaline ja kindel vahetus"

#: .\posts\templates\posts\index.html:207
msgid ""
"Found an expensive camera setup at a cafe. I was worried about scams, but "
"the built-in messaging let me verify the rightful owner safely by asking "
"them about the specific lens serial number."
msgstr ""
"Leidsin kohvikust kalli kaamerakomplekti. Kartsin kelmusi, kuid "
"sisseehitatud sõnumisüsteem võimaldas mul õiget omanikku turvaliselt "
"kontrollida, küsending temalt objektiivi konkreetset seerianumbrit."

